Author: chaotic_ass_neutral
Text: definitely food and water weight, believe me. As someone who actually gained back their hard work slowly but surely (2-3 months), it takes more than a couple days, even weeks.

Author: kangaroojackcoffee
Text: I went from 125-134 in 3 days! But the good news is that for the both of us, it is just water and sodium retention. Drink a bunch of water and be nice to yourself today and tomorrow and it should mostly go away.
